overview: When Mark Long hears what Damien Kyle is asking up front to move in, he realizes he's way out of his range. Damien sees an opportunity and tells Mark there may be another way for him to make his deposit. Markie More booked his beach rental not knowing the rental agent's son, Grayson Lange, would be stalking his every move. After waiting around for the better part of an hour, Leo becomes suspicious and Dalton finally confesses that there never was a buyer. He set up the meeting as an excuse to see Leo. Michael DelRay and boyfriend Jackson Traynor stumble upon an open house showing. Upon entering the kitchen, Michael gets a sneaky little idea in his head and convinces Jackson to go for it right there!
title: Raw Deposit
